title: Bathurst 12 Hour 2017: live results, updates | NT News
text:
Live: 2017 Liqui Moly Bathurst 12 Hour Will Dale, FOX SPORTS February 5, 2017 12:42pm 
WELCOME to our live coverage of the 2017 Liqui Moly Bathurst 12 Hour at Mount Panorama, Bathurst. 
Attrition has been high among the lead runners with crashes and mechanical woes accounting for several potential winners. 
At the halfway point, the battle for the lead appears to be between two cars: the No.22 Mercedes of Shane van Gisbergen/Maro Engel/Craig Baird and the No.88 Ferrari of Jamie Whincup/Craig Lowndes/Toni Vilander. 
Follow all the action with our live blog throughout the day.
